  <div class="app-card-container">
    <div class="card">
      <h1>About Me</h1>



      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image" %>

          <div class="skills">
            <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <div class="progress">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                    role="progressbar"
                    aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                    aria-valuemax="100"
                    style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>  
              </div>
            </div>
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>

            <% end %>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-8">
          <p>My name is Deven Clingman and I enjoy long walks on the beach and puppies... But that's not why you're here. You're here because you want a webiste built. I assure you that I would be able to provide you with website you need to improve your business.</p>
          <p>
            <button
              class="btn btn-primary"
              type="button"
              data-toggle="collapse"
              data-target="#jobHistory"
              aria-expanded="false"
              aria-controler="jobHistory"
            >
              Job History
            </button>

            <button
              class="btn btn-primary"
              type="button"
              data-toggle="collapse"
              data-target="#education"
              aria-expanded="false"
              aria-controler="education"
            >
              Education
            </button>

            <button
              class="btn btn-primary"
              type="button"
              data-toggle="collapse"
              data-target="#accomplishments"
              aria-expanded="false"
              aria-controler="accomplishments"
            >
              Accomplishments
            </button>
          </p>

          <p>
            <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
              <div class="card card-block">
                Job 1
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                Job 2
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="collapse" id="education">
              <div class="card card-block">
                School 1
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                School 2
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="collapse" id="accomplishments">
              <div class="card card-block">
                Once, single handedly defeated a Lion and his wives in defence of a small African village.
              </div>
              <div class="card card-block">
                Dug a hole from America to China while simultaniously cooking a delicous dinner for my wife. 
              </div>
            </div>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>